Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:54.21,Text-CN,,0,0,200,,{\fs40\fsp0}Oh,  and  lock  the  windows  when  you  leave.\N{\fs80\fsp3}还有走的时候记得关窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:56.77,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.26,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,住宿真麻烦
